1. *Fudbal* je najpopularniji sport u Srbiji. (Football is the most popular sport in Serbia.)
2. Svi igrači *fudbala* moraju nositi kopačke. (All football players must wear cleats.)
3. Naša ekipa igra protiv njihove u nedelju u *fudbalu*. (Our team is playing against theirs on Sunday in football.)
4. U mom kraju, *fudbal* se igra na asfaltu. (In my neighborhood, football is played on asphalt.)
5. Mogao bih gledati *fudbal* ceo dan. (I could watch football all day.)
6. Da li si ikada igrao *fudbal* sa svojim prijateljima? (Have you ever played football with your friends?)
7. Na stadionu ima mesta za deset hiljada navijača *fudbala*. (The stadium can hold up to ten thousand football fans.)
8. *Fudbal* je zabavan, ali i zahtevan sport. (Football is a fun, but demanding sport.)